\subtree{
\title{5. Machine Learning Integration}
\p{Build ML pipelines with transformers, encoders, and integration with scikit-learn, XGBoost, and other frameworks. Reference \code{\startverb references/machine_learning.md\stopverb} for:}

\ul{
